<div class="container">
  
<!-- START THE CAROUSEL -->
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-sm-12">
      <div id="myCarousel" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
        <ol class="carousel-indicators">
          <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="0" class="active"></li>
          <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="1"></li>
          <li data-target="#myCarousel" data-slide-to="2"></li>
        </ol>      
        <div class="carousel-inner" role="listbox">
          <div class="item active">
            <img class="first-slide" src="http://brainsoftgroup.com/images/vision.png" alt="First slide">
            <div class="container">
              <div class="carousel-caption">
                <h1>Sprout</h1>
                <h2>Let your dreams take root</h2>
                <% if !current_user %>
                <p><%= link_to "Sign Up today", new_user_registration_path, class: "btn btn-lg btn-primary" %></p>
                <% end %>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <img class="second-slide" src="http://brainsoftgroup.com/images/vision.png" alt="Second slide">
            <div class="container">
              <div class="carousel-caption">
                <h1>Create A Clear Vision of Your Ideal Destination</h1>
                <p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="#" role="button">Learn more</a></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <img class="third-slide" src="http://brainsoftgroup.com/images/vision.png" alt="Third slide">
            <div class="container">
              <div class="carousel-caption">
                <h1>Conquer The Challenges In Your Life</h3>
                <p><a class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" href="#" role="button">Browse gallery</a></p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a class="left carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="prev">
          <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-left" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
        </a>
        <a class="right carousel-control" href="#myCarousel" role="button" data-slide="next">
          <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-chevron-right" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="sr-only">Next</span>
        </a>
      </div><!-- /.carousel -->
    </div><!-- /.col-md-12 -->
  </div><!-- /.row -->
<!-- /END THE CAROUSEL -->  


<!-- START THE FEATURETTES -->
  <div class="row featurette">
    <hr class="featurette-divider">
    <div class="col-md-7 success-story-1">
      <h2 class="featurette-heading">Lisa Smith<span class="text-muted">, Graduate Student</span></h2>
      <p class="lead">"Sprout has not only helped me to achieve goals, but more importantly, it has enabled me to discover who I am, what makes me tick, and what those goals really are. Sprout was able to find the hidden treasures that allow me to achieve those goals."</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-5">
      <img class="featurette-image img-responsive center-block" src="http://cdn1.theodysseyonline.com/files/2015/06/04/635690584083999001-1832628294_635683512724816093-1684666009_IMG_6834.imgopt500x65.JPG">
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row featurette">
    <hr class="featurette-divider">
    <div class="col-md-7 col-md-push-5 success-story-2">
      <h2 class="featurette-heading">Jane Doe<span class="text-muted">, Administrator</span></h2>
      <p class="lead">"I'm so glad that I started this journey. In so many areas of my life I have been able to make huge strides. I have lost 30 pounds with the help of Sprout. Sprout reminded me of my values and coached me in a gentle but firm way. I am so grateful for all Sprout has done for me and I will be telling everyone who wants to achieve more (and even those who don't know they want to) about the difference using Sprout has made. My business has increased and is ever increasing. I am more confident than I have ever been. I feel I have moved mountains."</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-5 col-md-pull-7">
      <img class="featurette-image img-responsive center-block" src="https://tttphotos.s3.amazonaws.com/production/uploads/user/profileimage/50815/largesquare_Headshot_in_Purple_flipped_face0.jpg">
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row featurette">
    <hr class="featurette-divider">
    <div class="col-md-7 success-story-3">
      <h2 class="featurette-heading">John Doe<span class="text-muted">, Physician</span></h2>
      <p class="lead">"Sprout has helped me to identify issues that have stood in the way of business success and assisted me in developing techniques for working around or through these issues. As someone who has gone through substantial change in my professional career over the past couple of years, I count on sprout to ensure that this transition continues to go smoothly."</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-5">
      <img class="featurette-image img-responsive center-block" src="http://cms.ipressroom.com.s3.amazonaws.com/214/files/20150/55414b67f6091d5fbf000002_Paliwal_Headshot_500px/Paliwal_Headshot_500px_mid.jpg" alt="Generic placeholder image">
    </div>
    <hr class="featurette-divider">
  </div>
<!-- /END THE FEATURETTES -->
